description: The ID of the timesheet to associate this timecard entry with. All entries in a bulk request typically belong to the same timesheet. Construction timesheets represent a collection of time entries for a specific period, usually weekly. Timesheets go through a foreman/supervisor approval process before payroll processing, and multiple timecard entries are typically grouped under a single timesheet for batch processing. See [List Timesheets](https://developers.procore.com/reference/rest/v1/timesheets#list-timesheets) to retrieve available timesheets for your project.
